#: ../../../../sources/1.9/docs/intro/tutorial06.txt:84
msgid "Adding a background-image"
msgstr "背景画像を追加する"

#: ../../../../sources/1.9/docs/intro/tutorial06.txt:86
msgid ""
"Next, we'll create a subdirectory for images. Create an ``images`` "
